Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 到極限了 達利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差少許
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠應該…已經沒有核心…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 沒有支援…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉謝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件裝甲服的能量棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已經分散裝在裝甲服內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且應該已經完全充電
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何不先造我的裝甲服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人看來已經進化到…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人型時的核心也能活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把牠說成生物一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 Skyhook的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電荷擾亂了龍脈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠拖著龍脈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才有不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把牠跟龍脈分離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則 牠會不停復活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然… 我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼 格拉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止 不要說機械語言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你別忘記是我救你出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現我小小的心願 格拉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如何改變這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想親眼看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想成為神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神只會袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衪只會觀察著自己造出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有缺陷的生物成長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我的確是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你就像…神中之神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「Anti-seed」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了令金屬擁有獨立的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何都須要模仿人的那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史汀奇把你的seed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殖入自己女兒腦內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後藉此產生抗體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那只不過是開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在自己體內…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是自願的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的minor copy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我移殖了亞人的核心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來控制我體內的人工機器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成為最進化的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管如此 你也是人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白姐姐為何憎恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞…你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我的身體做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼大件沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不這麼大件便穿不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的裝甲服好像不大對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真的很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜只是一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便消滅了那麼大的亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的裝甲服的確很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 穿上身時…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上身時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個問題你不久便會給我解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽住…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一絲不掛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉謝爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞來了 他們在講話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你老爸到現在的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橫跨兩代 我一直受你們的恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指…我只是在利用你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別胡說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並非同情你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因我認為你的技術是優秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那怎麼算心願啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算一直以維修上一個世紀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汙染環境而嘈吵的車輛來終老嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是個大笑話啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全新概念的裝甲服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然是以你的生體數據為基礎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你的裝甲服是首先完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我希望你不要穿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經到了極限吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對一個已經成熟的女性來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝甲服的回饋給她的負擔太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你是擔心我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格…格拉迪亞…你做了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想成為神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡 你便能一直不停地觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直不停地觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把地底的蚯蚓放出來地面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行… 不可把龍脈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這年紀不玩玩具的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看見火光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心想我們見面時…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是穿得性感誘人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的傷沒大礙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是拒人於千里之外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像想把自己關起來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並非想為你做心理分析…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市內已經無人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 東京被封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外界害怕費挪現象會擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這班是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是國際聯合軍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的日本被占領了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被亞人和其他國家占領了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡…里昂…你留在這裡做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲 馬上來地下基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 有人在你身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒有啦 我現在沒那種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是說那種話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪獸…有怪獸出現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間等布烈絲來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞把龍脈變成生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定是想突破東京封鎖線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要制止她的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…第一次穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以離開一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇 這裡是女性專用的房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對吼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的拍檔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 他在家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AD警察已經解散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們奉命要離開東京
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你為何留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也已經沒有戰鬥的意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始便已經沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我你憎恨亞人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管我 很難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去裝甲服裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我放出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這過程很嘔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是inner metal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它會直接包裹你們的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很嘔心啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上便會凝固的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 發出指示
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿裝甲服是要唸咒語的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咒語 什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即是向inner metal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發出命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那須要你們在腦內…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把指示明確地轉化為語言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 我一這樣想 它便會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想強大起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跳得更高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲…厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成為非常威風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脫胎換骨的Knight Sabers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Knight Sabers 出動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞她們出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經阻止過她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也應該阻止她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只會白費唇舌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉謝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會一直幫助絲莉亞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能…無法一直在絲莉亞身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美臣博士招攬你 你也沒離開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…絲莉亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會繼續這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後亦永遠不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好像就是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇 我也出動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很嘔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成模擬生命體的龍脈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在令費挪現象擴散啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋪設在地底的全都變成失常亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  牠那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上次也獨自消滅了巨型亞人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在有三個人啊 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們合作得天衣無縫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠那麼想變成生物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想用亞人覆蓋全世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受了傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊…繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:23:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次好像已經是很久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟同伴一起短暫休息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿面笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才還在戰鬥好像不真實一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.85,0:24:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 現在乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.62,0:24:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.89,0:24:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡被亞人包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 吹波糖危機

